{
  "text": ") has received considerable attention in recent times for identification of mode of action. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] . Although a number of methodologically different in silico target prediction approaches exist, in the following we will limit our analysis to ligand-based target prediction algorithms that employs fingerprints combined with Bayes-based approaches.",
